text:
Jmeter version 2.9 is not backward compatible. I created from scratch a jmx file using version 2.9 just only using the existing components that were in a previous version (2.6). 

When trying to open the new test plan created in version 2.9 using the Jmeter 2.6 it gives this error: "Error in test plan - see log file".
